<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-06-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-06-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="675" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d675">
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-06-16"><hi rend="italic">June 16,
                                1896</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Resume duties to-day. Referring to your cablegram, received Paris, please
                            indicate what you would consider just decision <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi> case as basis for my efforts.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>